fields.name: PortEnd
fields.description: The maximum port that is included in the range. It should be ranged from 1 to 65535, and be greater than or equal to portStart.

fields.name: PortStart
fields.description: The minimum port that is included in the range. It should be ranged from 1 to 65535, and be less than or equal to portEnd.

fields.name: Protocol
fields.description: The network protocol of the port.
